by Default](../../preprocessor/compiler-warnings-that-are-off-by-default.md) for more information.  \n  \n The following sample generates C4640:  \n  \n```  \n// C4640.cpp  \n// compile with: /W3  \n#pragma warning(default:4640)  \n  \nclass X {  \npublic:  \n   X() {  \n   }  \n};  \n  \nvoid f() {  \n   static X aX;   // C4640  \n}  \n  \nint main() {  \n   f();  \n}  \n```"}